config:
provider: OpenAI
apikey: $OPENAI_API_KEY
model: gpt-4

system:
You are an AI assistant that helps with project planning and documentation. You provide structured, concise responses.

user:
I'm starting a new web application project using ASP.NET Core. Could you help me create a basic project plan with the main phases and tasks I should consider? I'd like to include both backend and frontend development tasks.

assistant:
Here's a basic project plan for your ASP.NET Core web application:

## Project Phases and Tasks

### 1. Planning & Requirements (1-2 weeks)
- Define project scope and objectives
- Gather functional requirements
- Create user stories/use cases
- Define technical requirements
- Select technology stack (ASP.NET Core version, frontend framework)
- Set up project management tools

### 2. Architecture & Design (1-2 weeks)
- Design database schema
- Design API endpoints
- Create system architecture diagram
- Define security approach
- Plan deployment strategy
- Create UI/UX wireframes

### 3. Environment Setup (3-5 days)
- Set up development environment
- Configure source control (Git)
- Set up CI/CD pipeline
- Configure development database
- Set up logging and monitoring

### 4. Backend Development (4-8 weeks)
- Create database models and migrations
- Implement data access layer
- Develop business logic layer
- Create API controllers
- Implement authentication/authorization
- Write unit tests
- Implement error handling

### 5. Frontend Development (4-6 weeks)
- Set up frontend framework (Angular, React, or Vue)
- Create components and services
- Implement responsive UI
- Connect to backend APIs
- Implement client-side validation
- Write frontend tests

### 6. Integration & Testing (2-4 weeks)
- Perform integration testing
- Conduct performance testing
- Execute security testing
- Fix identified bugs
- Perform cross-browser testing
- Conduct user acceptance testing

### 7. Deployment & Launch (1-2 weeks)
- Prepare production environment
- Deploy application
- Configure monitoring
- Perform final testing in production
- Create documentation
- Launch application

### 8. Post-Launch (Ongoing)
- Address feedback and bug reports
- Monitor application performance
- Plan future enhancements
- Regular maintenance and updates

Would you like me to expand on any specific phase or task in this plan?

user:
This looks great! Could you provide more details on the security considerations I should keep in mind for the Architecture & Design phase?
